we don't even have anything planned.

00:56.580 --> 00:58.445
I know,
but we talked about this.

00:58.450 --> 01:00.415
We're gonna take a trip
as soon as we have time.

01:00.416 --> 01:01.979
- I promise.
- Just like you promised

01:01.980 --> 01:03.050
