the "Bumblebee" movie?

01:03.051 --> 01:05.144
I didn't promise that.
I believe what I said was,

01:05.144 --> 01:06.259
"Isn't that a kids' movie?"

01:06.260 --> 01:08.019
Yeah, and I believe
what I said was,

01:08.020 --> 01:10.510
"It's for teens."

01:10.511 --> 01:12.957
Look, I get that you can't
take any time off from work,

01:12.960 --> 01:15.300
