- Well, just the kids thing.

05:30.979 --> 05:32.329
Saying that we were gonna
start trying soon.

05:32.369 --> 05:34.639
Oh, I'm sorry.
I didn't mean right away.

05:34.679 --> 05:36.989
I just meant in the near future.

05:37.029 --> 05:38.989
Oh.
Okay.

05:39.029 --> 05:40.249
Cool, cool, cool,
cool, cool, cool.

05:40.299 --> 05:41.599
Cool, cool, cool, cool,

05:41.639 --> 05:42.989
except for that there's
one little problem there,

05:43.039 --> 05:44.869
which is that I don't know
that I totally know

05:44.909 --> 05:46.855
that I for sure
want to have kids,

05:48.059 --> 05:49.569
so...

05:49.609 --> 05:51.649
- You don't?
- No.

05:51.699 --> 05:54.219
- Do you?
- Uhhuh.

05:54.269 --> 05:56.619
Oh.

05:57.761 --> 05:58.801
I don't understand.
I thought we were

05:58.841 --> 06:00.170
